select a.property_id,a.metaname_id,m.metaname_name,a.indicator_id,a.asset_id, a.opt_answer_id,a.answer,o.answer_classification from answers a,optional_answers o,metanames m where a.indicator_id=o.indicator_id and a.metaname_id=m.id and a.opt_answer_id=o.id and a.datex="2024-11-10"

select a.property_id,a.metaname_id,m.metaname_name,a.indicator_id,a.asset_id, a.opt_answer_id,a.answer,o.answer_classification from answers a,optional_answers o,metanames m where a.indicator_id=o.indicator_id and a.metaname_id=m.id and a.opt_answer_id=o.id and WEEK(a.datex)=WEEK(NOW())
